lead_paragraph: Everton moved up to third place in the Premier League despite being held to a 1-1 draw by Crystal Palace as Belgium strikers Christian Benteke and Romelu Lukaku both got on the scoresheet in a battling encounter on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Everton Up to Third Despite Being Held by Palace
headline.main: Everton Up to Third Despite Being Held by Palace
